N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 111.6 - Handling of crop prior to inspection

State Regulations

Establishment and maintenance of isolation strips, removal of undesirable individual trees, and marking of seed production area as
hereinafter described, are to be completed previous to field
inspections. Notes
